.TH FINDDEPS 1 "PKGMAINT-#VERSION# Manual"

.SH NAME
finddeps - find linked dependencies for a package

.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBfinddeps\fR \fIPKG\fR

.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBfinddeps\fR lists dependencies of dynamic executables and libraries
of the installed package. It parsing the output of the \fBldd\fR(1)
command.

\fBfinddeps\fP operates on installed packages and requires
\fBpkginfo\fR(8).

.SH SEE ALSO
\fBfindredundantdeps\fR(8), \fBpkginfo\fP(8)
